      "date": "2011-05-30 09:54:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nUnder the failover configuration described in LU-372, replay-single test 61d, 85, 87 failed as follows:\n\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/172b0dd4-8745-11e0-b4df-52540025f9af\n\nWith the patch, the tests passed:\n\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8863f6e0-8804-11e0-b4df-52540025f9af\n\nAnd here are the passed results for other failover/recovery tests with the patch applied:\n\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/835c5eb2-8804-11e0-b4df-52540025f9af\n\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/ef7865fe-8814-11e0-b4df-52540025f9af",
